<div class="entry-content"><p>With endless possibilities and beautiful surroundings, Camp Tanuga offers a unique alternative to your typical event setting. We have vast experience in hosting private parties, reunions, weekend retreats, sports camps, corporate picnics and training seminars. We look forward to accommodating your needs and dreams.</p>
<p>Our facilities are generally available in May, early June, August and September.</p>
